Full Description: Advanced Network Devices (AND) provides best-in-class IP endpoints and advanced network products for use in paging, intercom, and synchronized clocks for integration into Unified Communications (UC) systems and mass notification applications such as schools, office buildings, hospitals, sports complexes, and many others. AND specializes in advanced audio and video applications, especially those relating to networking, notification, security and time keeping. AND supports standard protocols, such as SIP, as well as API integration with UC software providers. Their products are developed with flexibility and interoperability in mind. Flexibility combined with a multi-function device connected and powered by a single network cable adds value while eliminating cost. Having sold IP speakers since 2004, AND is an early adopter of the PoE solutions. AND provided audio over Ethernet before most, and was one of the first, if not the first provider of PoE IP loudspeaker. The technology is mature and long proven, which facilitates a low-cost, stable product with a rich set of features. AND has the know-how to handle a wide variety of network situations and can facilitate custom requests. AND has a comprehensive portfolio of PoE endpoints to match your IP message notification needs, backed up by an organization committed to providing best-in-class engineering services. Their products are designed and manufactured in the United States. If you can’t find what you are looking for in their standard products, they invite you to explore what other solutions they can provide you with.
